903
00:49:14.282 --> 00:49:17.411
Richard Jewell, 33 let, bivši policist,

904
00:49:17.494 --> 00:49:19.663
ustreza profilu samotnega bombaša.

905
00:49:19.746 --> 00:49:22.332
