906
00:49:22.416 --> 00:49:24.001
ki je bivši policist,

907
00:49:24.084 --> 00:49:27.212
bivši vojak ali pa je imel željo,
da postane policist,


908
00:49:27.296 --> 00:49:28.922
in želi biti junak.

909
00:49:29.965 --> 00:49:32.259
Jewell je po eksploziji bombe
postal zvezdnik.


910
00:49:32.342 --> 00:49:34.177
Nastopal je v <i>The Today Showu."</i>

911
00:49:34.261 --> 00:49:35.637
FBI ve, da imaš to?

912
00:49:36.138 --> 00:49:37.973
Ja, moj vir pravi, da vsi vedo.

913
00:49:38.056 --> 00:49:39.433
TV-mreže vedo.

914
00:49:40.058 --> 00:49:41.268
CNN ve.

915
00:49:41.351 --> 00:49:44.730
Tip pri GBI pravi enako.
